   <S PAR='1' RSNT='1' SNO='1'>CHAPTER TEN ONCE A YEAR THROUGH THE BIBLE EXPLANATION</S>
   <S PAR='2' RSNT='1' SNO='2'>1 The purpose of this book is to help the believers in their daily study of the Bible.</S>
   <S PAR='3' RSNT='1' SNO='3'>If the reader goes through the daily assigned portions of the Old and the New Testament, he will read through the entire Bible in one year.</S>
   <S PAR='4' RSNT='1' SNO='4'>2 As a special feature, this book allows the reader to understand the main significance of each book of the Bible as well as the meaning in each book's sections.</S>
